<h2>
    Fly Fishing for Pink Salmon
</h2>
<p>
    Fly fishing for pink salmon near Salem is an increasingly popular approach, especially on smaller tributaries. Their aggressive nature during the spawn makes them great targets for well-presented flies.
</p>
<p>
    <strong>Recommended Fly Setups:</strong>
</p>
<ul>
