    <li>
        <strong>Line</strong>: Floating line with short sink-tip or intermediate sink line
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Leader</strong>: 6–10 lb fluorocarbon
    </li>
</ul>
<p>
    <strong>Best Fly Patterns:</strong>
</p>
<ul>
    <li>
